These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, tea
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, peach, plum, radish
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, october, april, september
City: berlin, hannover, san-francisco, marseilles
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, indian, australian, japanese
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, climbing, rugby, skiing
 1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far right##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is the egyptian##1
 3. the indian is on the left of the australian##1
 4. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 5. the person drinking tea is the person eating radish##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 7. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the person who's sport is baseball and the japanese##2
 8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 9. the egyptian is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person eating radish##2
11. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
12. the person traveling to marseilles is the person who's birthday is in september##1
13. the australian is between the indian and the person who's birthday is in april##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | tea        | coffee       | lemonade  | almond-milk |
| Food          | radish     | plum         | peach     | broccoli    |
| Birthday         | october  | july      | april   | september     |
| City           | hannover | berlin | san-francisco   | marseilles     |
| Nationality   | indian    | australian         | egyptian | japanese         |
| Sport         | skiing     | baseball     | climbing  | rugby       |

