.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, swimming, golf, rugby
4 different pets are kept: hamster, horse, rat, goat
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, thriller, time-travel, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, folk, gospel
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, azure, ebony, aquamarine
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, ship, train
 1. the person who likes azure is between the owner of the rat and the person driving the bike##2
 2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 3. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
 4. the person who likes azure is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person driving the ship##2
 5. the fan of disco is the person who's sport is swimming##1
 6. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
 7. the owner of the horse is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person watching action movies and the owner of the goat##2
 9. the person watching thriller movies is the owner of the goat##1
10. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1
11. the fan of disco is the person watching time-travel movies##1
12. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
13. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
14. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who likes azure##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Sport      | rugby    | swimming       | golf   | sailing |
| Pet         | hamster     | rat   | goat    | horse  |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | time-travel | thriller   | western     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | disco       | electronic | folk        |
| Color   | aquamarine | ebony   | azure     | brown    |
| Transport     | bus       | ship        | train      | bike        |

