The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, family, scientific
There are 4 different nationalities: american, french, malaysian, russian
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, subway, taxi
 1. the fan of disco is between the modern house and the malaysian##2
 2. the fan of pop is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 4. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of disco##1
 5. the russian is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 6. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the american##1
 8. the person driving the subway is the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person driving the car is between the owner of the hedgehog and the craftsman house##2
10. the malaysian is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
11. the craftsman house is on the left of the person driving the car##1
12. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the fan of soul##1
13. the fan of pop is the fan of pop##1
14. the townhouse house is the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |         2          |     3      |     4     |
