 1. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 2. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
 5. the person traveling to venice is on the far right##1
 6. the fan of soul is between the person who likes fuchsia and the person eating zucchini##2
 7. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the airplane is the person eating blueberry##1
10. the person who likes white is the person traveling to miami##1
